<lb ed="B" n="0174b16"/>西至秦淮河北至鷄籠山</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0174b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">外永福寺</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>外永福寺</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0174b18"/><p xml:id="pB29p0174b1801" style="margin-left:1em">在郭城上方門外泉水鄉東城地西去所領定林寺十
<lb ed="B" n="0174b19"/>里北去正陽門四十里</p>
